            "subtitle": "Computer Science Researcher (Dr.)",
            "text": "<p className='mb-4'>Hi,<p>I am passionate about using <b>analytics</b> and <b>AI</b> to unlock insights from complex datasets. With over <b>12 years of experience</b> (in data analysis and software development), I specialize in creating and optimizing <b>practical solutions</b> for real-world problems.</p><p>Additionally, I bring a <b>strong academic background (PhD)</b> and enjoy contributing to the design and delivery of training programs to share knowledge with others.</p></p>",
